  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support 300 Kids with Learning Disabilities in Imo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In AFRYDEF, we see children and youths as assets, and do our best to encourage them develop their full potentials. The above project is aimed at providing 5 toilets/bathrooms and medical care for the 300+ children at the Special Education Center, Imo State, Nigeria.  To achieve these, we shall engage 5 nurses and 5 care givers at the center to provide medical care and support to the children, including cleaning their beds, cutting their hairs/nails as well as take care of their sanitary needs.</narrative>
  </description>
